[thinking] **Exploring GraalVM native-image options**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering how to add import Test and JVM arguments, as well as build arguments under graalvmNative. I want to see if I can make the native-image allow for reflection. However, the runtime module openings might not be the same. It seems important to know that buildArgs pass to native-image but not to the runtime. I'll need to think about how existing Netty uses these features to ensure compatibility.
